Subject: Beast Wrestler (Sega Genesis) 
To: Cliff
Content:
Beast Wrestler (Sega Genesis) is a one on one wrestling game developed by Telenet Japan and published by Renovation Products in 1991 for the Mega Drive systems. The game features a total of 20 different beasts who appear throughout the game. It features both one player and two player modes.
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
